table CommitmentDocumentTable
	lineageTag: 78008f31-f28e-4b67-82ac-ce64379f182c

	measure DocumentsIsRowVisible = ```
			
			VAR StartDate = [StartDate]
			VAR EndDate = [EndDate]
			VAR CurrentDate = SELECTEDVALUE(CommitmentDocumentTable[Date])
			RETURN
			IF(
			    NOT(ISBLANK(CurrentDate)) 
			    && CurrentDate >= StartDate 
			    && CurrentDate <= EndDate,
			    1,
			    0
			)
			```
		formatString: 0
		lineageTag: 4431126a-7e19-4a52-8405-17973474cb6b

